author: By GARY D. ROBERTSON Associated Press
title: Doctor: 2 weeks for North Carolina order to take slow cases
description: RALEIGH, N.C. (AP) — North Carolina's new stay-at-home order won't show any conclusive effect on blunting the intensity of the new coronavirus for about two weeks, the state epidemiologist said Monday.
